comments: If it wasn\'t for Mr.Denise, I never would have accepted "The Mole"! Thanks, Mr. Denise!

I hated Chemistry. Still don\'t like it but look foward to this class every week. He has helped me actually understand chem. Never thought in a million yrs I\'d be getting an A but thanks to him I am. Still not an "easy" class but he teaches and explains concepts well....

Completely dreaded taking this mandatory class. So thankful I got Mr.Denise! Because of him, I have a newer understanding and love for Chemistry! He is a bit random at times but that is what makes his class so much fun! He will make sure you understand everything before you leave class! He\'s also got a GREAT haircut!
lots of energy, in a good way. makes class more enjoyable. tries to share concepts to make material fit everyday situations.
